commits.message:
Fixes issue #2038
Chart end date in PNG/JPEG export is not respected
Fixed: annoying signins when choosing "until GanttProject is closed" token validity

issue.title: Chart end date in PNG/JPEG export is not respected
issue.body:
Hello,
I notice that when exporting in JPEG format, the end date is not respected and there are days/weeks in addition.
Thank you for your help.

comment.body: Having the same problem here. Will this be fixed in the next release?
